Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:14.37,Prism Jump 粉色,,0,0,0,,{\fscx65\fscy65\blur3}Heartful Splash
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,棒極了
